<h1 class="cd-text cd-title">navigation</h1>
<p class="cd-text">Below are our core navigation components that should be use to direct a user around a website or collection of subpages.</p>

<h2 class="cd-text cd-title">default nav</h2>
<p class="cd-text">Our default in-page nav is a horizontal nav with pill styling. The <code>.nav__item--active</code> class can optionally be used to highlight the current context.</p>

{{{ getFile 'site/docs/views/examples/nav/sub-nav.html' }}}
