<h2 class="cd-text cd-title">small tabbed nav</h2>
<p class="cd-text">Use the <code>.nav--tabs--sm</code> modifier to generate a tabbed nav with less padding.</p>
{{{ getFile 'site/docs/views/examples/nav/nav-tabs-sm.html' }}}
