{{/codeBlock}}

<h2 class="cd-text cd-title">inverse tabbed nav</h2>
<p class="cd-text">Use the <code>.nav--tabs--inverse</code> modifier to generate a tabbed nav that works on dark backgrounds.</p>
{{{ getFile 'site/docs/views/examples/nav/nav-tabs-inverse.html' }}}
{{#codeBlock}}
    {{{ getFile 'site/docs/views/examples/nav/nav-tabs-inverse.html' }}}
{{/codeBlock}}

<h2 class="cd-text cd-title">tabbed nav as dropdown menu</h2>
<p class="cd-text">Adds down chevrons to tabs to indicate they activate a drop down menu. This is really only intended for use when across the full width of a page so please refer to the <a href="/layouts/drop-down-menu">dropdown menu example page</a> for an example.</p>

{{{ getFile 'site/docs/views/examples/nav/nav-tabs-dd.html' }}}

